{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "战火之霸道 第12章 EX1-1 兄妹",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "不久前，莱昂尼多、法尔艾斯和谢斯三人\\n在旧王都索尔·阿尔贝里亚进行了一场对话。\\n莱昂尼多和谢斯对于法尔艾斯抱有怀疑，\\n便对其进行追问，但法尔艾斯却轻描淡写地\\n表示“只是走我自己的路而已”。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "不久前——\\n旧王都索尔·阿尔贝里亚",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "喔？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，真巧啊。\\n这不是莱昂尼多王兄\\n和法尔艾斯王兄嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "是啊，还真是巧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我们难得碰面，\\n要不要找个地方聊聊天？\\n毕竟这样的机会也不多。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "行吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "哦？真令人意外。\\n我还以为以莱昂尼多的性格，\\n会以无聊为由拒绝呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我只是有些事想问问你们。\\n仅此而已……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "那么，我们聊什么好呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "王兄可真会说笑。现在的我们\\n感兴趣的事也就那么几件吧。\\n比如说……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "比如说……\\n为什么与魔神联手？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "真不愧是法尔艾斯王兄。\\n如你所说，的确令人在意呢。\\n尤其是莱昂尼多王兄。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我从来没想过莱昂尼多王兄\\n会屈居他人之下。\\n我很好奇这究竟是出于什么目的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼……你大可以让她去查啊，\\n你那引以为傲的“小猫咪”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀！说出这种讽刺的话\\n可不像是你的风格呢。\\n我戳到你的痛处了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "那么你又如何呢，谢斯？\\n我认为你的态度\\n更不可思议呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "是啊……\\n虽然这其中有很多原因，\\n但帝国的统治让我很感兴趣。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嚯？它可是背负着\\n“邪恶帝国”的恶名哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "拥有权力的职责之一，\\n就是聚集财富并进行再分配。\\n从某处聚集多少，再分配给某处多少。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "现在不过是分配比率与以往不同。\\n我了解到王都的情况之后，\\n还有点惊讶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嗯……这里一片祥和，\\n不像是邪恶帝国的首都。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "没错。魔神的确会夺走很多东西。\\n但也有人因此而得到恩惠。\\n说白了，这只是很普通的权力执行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我不禁认为，\\n魔神统治的国家也不过如此。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我倒是听说王都以外的地区\\n贫困状况越来越严重？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "嗯。可是王都内\\n并没有民众因此悲天悯人。\\n这就是人的欲望吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "对民众的欲望加以控制\\n也是当权者需要重视的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "陛下在王都的口碑也很不错，\\n真令人羡慕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "哦？这就是你\\n站在魔神这边的理由吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "这可不好说呢。\\n但我很喜欢被人们赞赏。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "呵呵，你这一点\\n还是和以前一样呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，恕我直言，\\n不觉得我变得更淑女了吗？\\n对吧，莱昂尼多王兄？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我哪知道。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "真是的，好冷淡啊。\\n倒是让我想起了以前……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "莱昂尼多王兄和法尔艾斯王兄\\n在一起的时候，只要我一靠近，\\n就马上会说我碍事呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "的确，有过那样的时期吧。\\n但即使是那样，\\n谢斯也总是凑过来呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "说起来，我们三个\\n好久没有聚在一起说话了。\\n上次聊天都是什么时候的事了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "是啊……应该是\\n父王还在世的时候吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "对了，说到父王，\\n我倒是有一个疑问。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "父王是因为看到供奉在\\n王城内的“圣片”开始浑浊，\\n才想要寻找新的“圣片”的吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嗯，我听说是这样。\\n怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "其实，\\n直到父王去封印遗迹为止，\\n我都没听说过“圣片”浑浊的事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你是想问，\\n“圣片”遍布阿尔贝里亚各地，\\n为什么王城内的圣片最先变浑浊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "对。王城内的不该是\\n最后才变浑浊吗？就算不是最后，\\n至少也该比封印遗迹的“圣片”晚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "关于这件事，我一直\\n都想请教法尔艾斯王兄。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "嗯，我觉得法尔艾斯王兄\\n应该对这种事最了解。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "是吗？关于“圣片”，\\n我的确是研究了个大概，\\n但并没有什么值得一提的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "这样啊，那真是遗憾。\\n我还以为法尔艾斯王兄\\n会知道一些内情呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "啊……辜负了你的期望，\\n真是抱歉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "谢斯，够了。\\n再怎么试探他也是徒劳。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我就开门见山地问吧，\\n法尔艾斯，你到底在想什么？\\n你不打算屈服于魔神吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我的想法以前就说过了，\\n我对善与恶不感兴趣。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "对我来说唯一重要的，\\n就只有选择有效的道路\\n去实现我的心愿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "那么，你的心愿是什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "改革。不，应该说是进化吧。\\n或者也可以说是创造。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "说了一堆模棱两可的词……\\n是想糊弄我们吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我可没有这种打算。\\n我只是不知道要怎么\\n用语言去描述而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "那么，你就具体说一说\\n接下来打算做什么吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我想想啊……总之，\\n我打算借助兄弟的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "兄弟？到底要向谁……\\n嗯！？你这家伙！该不会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你知道这会带来\\n什么样的后果吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我只是走自己的路而已。\\n你们也请便。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "如果我们的道路会在某一刻相汇，\\n那就届时再见吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}